{"tid":2428044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港父（安靜）","createTime":"2021-03-01T09:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T18:31:51.000Z","uid":154406,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c574028f1b20f350c34ee29610b96d2a627c94","tid":2428044,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"只剩下西西陪我吵了一天<br />\n睡著的這港父 安靜的潛水了<br />\n我想他已表現的非常明白<br />\n沒吹的十二碼 曼沒有靠黑哨<br />\n<br />\n你說你也會扮訓我不相信<br />\n曾陪著我大戰 也只是曾經<br />\n希望他是真的睡了沒有Mon Po<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1wKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=93d40ee9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n他才會逼自己睡覺<br />\n<br />\n你要我說多難堪 我根本正義之師<br />\n為什麼功夫足球都不能贏波<br />\n我沒有這種天份 保護這英超球證<br />\n不用擔心的太多 我在水底好好過<br />\n<br />\n港父已遠遠離開 明叔也慢慢走開<br />\n為什麼今晚波台沒有了罵戰<br />\n我沒有想到港父 安靜的竟這麼快<br />\n我會學著原諒你 是因為我太正義"},{"pid":"cb42db48faf491378c5eaf4f4893e42a88ed6003","tid":2428044,"uid":154406,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7in85o0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7in85o0.gif&h=a0164a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit to 會員冰人"},{"pid":"4a1bef77589ba616403bca32cc530ae30895596f","tid":2428044,"uid":1734,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb42db48faf491378c5eaf4f4893e42a88ed6003","tid":2428044,"uid":154406,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7in85o0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7in85o0.gif&h=a0164a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit to 會員冰人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"冰人連迪路夫？"},{"pid":"6b4dcd0d6190eb0661f51e6be55083cb04f4c6c2","tid":2428044,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:24:31.000Z","msg"